Notes: Staging applies to this quota .  If 80% of the quota is used, the UK will be obliged to offer an extra 136 tonnes/year, to a maximum level of 817 tonnes.

These three quotas are linked.  When volume is used under any quota, that amount is deducted from all three quotas.  They are administered as three separate quotas, because a different coefficient is applicable to calculate the carcass weight equivalent of differnt commodities.
